'''印尼高速鐵路'''（'''[[印尼语|印尼语]]'''：'''kereta api berkecepatan tinggi di Indonesia'''，又称'''雅万高铁'''）。是一条連接[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]]首都[[雅加達|雅加達]]和[[西爪哇省|西爪哇省]]的省会[[萬隆|萬隆]]的[[高速铁路|高速铁路]]。全長150公里，並有可能再延長至印尼第二大城，[[東爪哇省|東爪哇省]]的[[泗水_(印尼)|泗水]]<ref >{{cite news| date=1 October 2015| title=印尼叫停雅万高铁 或为雅加达-泗水高铁试水| url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/world/20150908/023423180915.shtml| accessdate=4 October 2015| archive-date=2021-02-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207162331/http://finance.sina.com.cn/world/20150908/023423180915.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>。是印尼正在建設的首條高鐵的路線。设计时速350公里<ref>{{Cite web |title=雅万高铁建设取得重要进展！全线13座隧道全部贯通 |url=http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NTc3MTgwMA==&mid=2651154498&idx=1&sn=e73010e9dceedf547389276faaad5836&chksm=bd02acb58a7525a3ad67c3814799b01d9144eaebb99af76f07091a6a9a08cf7f8d5aef157c7d#rd |website=微信公众平台 |access-date=2022-06-21}}</ref>。

== 發展歷程 ==
2015年7月，印尼的高速鐵路計劃公佈<ref name="Mail">{{cite news |title=INDONESIA PRESS-Govt to hold "beauty contest" for high-speed train project - Jakarta Globe |date=14 July 2015 |newspaper=Daily Mail |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/reuters/article-3160185/INDONESIA-PRESS-Govt-hold-beauty-contest-high-speed-train-project--Jakarta-Globe.html |accessdate=1 October 2015 |archive-date=2021-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222112757/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/reuters/article-3160185/INDONESIA-PRESS-Govt-hold-beauty-contest-high-speed-train-project--Jakarta-Globe.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。印尼首條高鐵的路線規劃為連接首都[[雅加達|雅加達]]和[[西爪哇省|西爪哇省]]的省会[[萬隆|萬隆]]，全長150公里，並有可能再延長至印尼第二大城，[[東爪哇省|東爪哇省]]的[[泗水_(印尼)|泗水]]<ref >{{cite news| date=1 October 2015| title=印尼叫停雅万高铁 或为雅加达-泗水高铁试水| url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/world/20150908/023423180915.shtml| accessdate=4 October 2015| archive-date=2021-02-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207162331/http://finance.sina.com.cn/world/20150908/023423180915.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[中华人民共和国高速铁路|中國]]和[[新幹線|日本]]都已經表達對項目的興趣，並進行了各自的調查<ref name="Mail"/>。此項印尼高鐵投標令中日在基建項目的競爭趨向白熱化<ref name="Forbes1">{{cite news | date=1 October 2015 | title=Japan's Rail Project Loss To China: Why It Matters For Abe's Economic Diplomacy And For China's | first=Stephen | last=Harner | url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/stephenharner/2015/10/01/japans-rail-project-loss-to-china-why-it-matters-for-abes-economic-diplomacy-and-for-chinas/ | accessdate=4 October 2015 | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108164435/https://www.forbes.com/sites/stephenharner/2015/10/01/japans-rail-project-loss-to-china-why-it-matters-for-abes-economic-diplomacy-and-for-chinas/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年9月下旬，印尼宣布將此項目批給中國<ref>{{cite news|date=29 September 2015|title=Indonesia to award fast train contract to China - Japanese embassy official|newspaper=Reuters|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/09/29/indonesia-railway-idUSL3N11Z3HQ20150929|accessdate=1 October 2015|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002165345/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/09/29/indonesia-railway-idUSL3N11Z3HQ20150929|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="ABC">{{cite news |title=Indonesia awards multi-billion-dollar railway project to China over Japan |date=30 September 2015 |newspaper=ABC |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-09-30/indonesia-awards-major-rail-contract-to-china/6818082 |accessdate=1 October 2015 |archive-date=2019-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190523183110/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-09-30/indonesia-awards-major-rail-contract-to-china/6818082 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，令日本失望<ref name="FT">{{cite news |date=1 October 2015 |title=Japan cries foul after Indonesia awards rail contract to China |author=Robin Harding in Tokyo, Avantika Chilkoti in Jakarta and Tom Mitchell in Beijing |newspaper=Financial Times |url=http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/eca4af84-67fa-11e5-97d0-1456a776a4f5.html#axzz3nL45xCH2 |accessdate=1 October 2015 |archive-date=2020-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417135723/http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/eca4af84-67fa-11e5-97d0-1456a776a4f5.html#axzz3nL45xCH2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。印尼方面指中國的計劃不需要借貸，亦不需要印尼的資助是印尼偏向中國的主因<ref name="Diplo">{{cite news |title=It's Official: China, Not Japan, Is Building Indonesia's First High-Speed Railway |author=Shannon Tiezzi |date=1 October 2015 |newspaper=The Diplomat |url=http://thediplomat.com/2015/10/its-official-china-not-japan-is-building-indonesias-first-high-speed-railway/ |accessdate=1 October 2015 |archive-date=2019-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190516055623/https://thediplomat.com/2015/10/its-official-china-not-japan-is-building-indonesias-first-high-speed-railway/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BSpec">{{cite news |title=China's high-speed rail bet pays off |author=Peter Cai |date=2 October 2015 |newspaper=Business Spectator |url=http://www.businessspectator.com.au/article/2015/10/2/china/chinas-high-speed-rail-bet-pays |accessdate=2 October 2015 |archive-date=2020-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417135731/http://www.businessspectator.com.au/article/2015/10/2/china/chinas-high-speed-rail-bet-pays |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是最後[[印尼|印尼]]因經費不足，拒絕兩國的方案，印尼政府認為不需要興建高鐵，中速鐵路就能滿足需求，希望兩國再提交中速鐵路新方案<ref>{{cite web|author=張渝萍|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20150905/36761756/|title=印尼高鐵突喊停 中日搶蓋落空|work=臺灣蘋果日報|access-date=2015-09-29|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810051443/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20150905/36761756/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年9月29日，印尼決定採用中國的200km/hr中高速鐵路方案<ref>{{cite web|author=楊明珠|url=http://appweb.cna.com.tw/webm/menu/afe/201509290271.aspx|title=印尼高鐵將採陸方案 日：遺憾至極|work=中央社|access-date=2015-09-29|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191606/http://appweb.cna.com.tw/webm/menu/afe/201509290271.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。日本[[內閣官房長官|內閣官房長官]][[菅義偉|菅義偉]]表示印尼提出無需加重政府的財政債務和債務擔保的情況下興建高速鐵路是超出常識<ref>{{cite news |date=2015-09-30 |title=印尼表示採用中國高鐵方案 |newspaper=日本經濟新聞中文版 |url=http://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/manufacturing/16356-20150930.html |accessdate=21 January 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072725/http://zh.cn.nikkei.com/industry/manufacturing/16356-20150930.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。鐵路計劃於2015年末開工，並計劃於2019年通車<ref name="WSJ">{{cite news |title=Indonesia’s Handling of High-Speed Train Project Adds to Business Confusion, Mixed messages to Japan, China come as Indonesia courts foreign investors |author=Ben Otto and Anita Rachman |date=30 September 2015 |newspaper=The Wall Street Journal |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/indonesia-to-break-ground-on-first-high-speed-railway-this-year-1443596942?mod=rss_Business |accessdate=1 October 2015 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801153042/https://www.wsj.com/articles/indonesia-to-break-ground-on-first-high-speed-railway-this-year-1443596942?mod=rss_Business |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年10月1日晚間，印尼國有企業部長[[丽妮·玛丽亚妮·苏马尔诺·苏万迪|莉妮]]於首都雅加達表示，目前選擇是中國提出的雅加達－萬隆高鐵方案，國企部已成立小組與中方針對項目合約細節進行商談，最快十月底可簽署協議，她強調，雅萬高鐵建設專案最終選擇中國方案，技術不是唯一標準，中國所提出的融資結構與無需政府擔保的方案、更吸引印尼政府；而[[印尼政府|印尼政府]]對[[高鐵|高鐵]]建設秉持著不占用國家預算及無需政府提供擔保的立場，何況雅萬高鐵從建設到營運，將會以公司聯合體的商業模式運作，並非由印尼政府作出最終抉擇。<ref>{{cite web|author=聯合報 大陸新聞中心|url=http://udn.com/news/story/6809/1226023-aspx|title=印尼高鐵爭奪戰 中國祭優惠搶贏日本|work=聯合報|access-date=2015-12-19|archive-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517023436/https://udn.com/news/story/6809/1226023-aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前铁路施工已按照中国方案进行施工<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com//world/2017-04/04/c_129524595.htm|title=雅万高铁进入全面实施阶段-新华网|accessdate=2019-05-21|work=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820175631/http://www.xinhuanet.com//world/2017-04/04/c_129524595.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，自2018年起进入全面施工状态<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2018-09/29/content_5326759.htm?_zbs_baidu_bk|title=中国出口印尼雅万高铁的盾构机下线_滚动新闻_中国政府网|accessdate=2019-05-21|work=www.gov.cn|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820171407/http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2018-09/29/content_5326759.htm?_zbs_baidu_bk|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-05/14/c_1124494049.htm|title=印尼雅万高铁重点工程瓦利尼隧道贯通-新华网|accessdate=2019-05-21|work=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806193813/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-05/14/c_1124494049.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年5月14日，雅万高铁瓦利尼隧道顺利贯通，[[中国驻印度尼西亚大使列表#_中华人民共和国驻印度尼西亚共和国大使（1990年至今）|中国驻印尼大使]][[肖千|肖千]]出席贯通仪式<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Bk8SUzJwBhW53qybUMqAAQ|title=首条隧道贯通！印尼雅万高铁取得重要进展|accessdate=2019-05-22|author=|date=2019-05-17|publisher=[[中国铁路总公司|中国铁路总公司]]微信公众号}}</ref>。

2021年12月5日，{{tsl|en|BeritaSatu|第一新聞}}等印尼媒體報導，承建雅萬高鐵工程的印尼中國高鐵公司（{{lang|en|Kereta Cepat Indonesia China}}，{{lang|en|KCIC}}）表示，倒塌的DK46號橋墩位於西爪哇省{{tsl|en|Karawang|卡拉旺縣}}特魯克姜比（Teluk Jambe），此意外並沒造成人員傷亡。印尼中國高鐵公司表示，工程監督團隊發現該橋墩出現位置偏差，要求當地營建商拆除重建，但由於營建商在拆除過程中並未遵守標準作業程序導致出現此次意外事件<ref>{{Cite web |url= https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php7?news_id=2142149& |title= 恐怖瞬間！印尼雅萬高鐵橋墩搬移倒塌　工人狂奔逃命 |accessdate= 2021-12-11 |author=  |date= 2021-12-09 |publisher= ETtoday新聞雲 |archive-date= 2021-12-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211211154203/https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php7?news_id=2142149& |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

==路線==
高鐵路線將東西橫貫[[爪哇島|爪哇島]]，連接首都[[雅加達|雅加達]]和[[東爪哇省|東爪哇省]]省會泗水。一期將優先建設首都雅加達至印度尼西亞第三大城市-西爪哇省省會萬隆間的約150公里的路段，預計投資約56.4億美元，建成後[[雅加達|雅加達]]-[[萬隆|萬隆]]的時間將縮短至40分鐘，整個高鐵建成後，[[雅加達|雅加達]]到[[泗水_(印尼)|泗水]]的時間將縮短至3小時。<ref>{{cite web|author=热点地理|url=http://www.hotdili.com/html/2547.html aspx|title=印尼爪洼岛高铁路线图和规划图|work=热点地理|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717115721/http://www.hotdili.com/html/2547.html|archivedate=2015-07-17|accessdate=2020-12-30}}</ref>

== 使用列車 ==
2021年1月15日，[[中国中铁|中国中铁]]在建的[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]]的[[印尼高速鐵路|雅万高铁]]项目 “云开放日”暨《中国中铁印度尼西亚社会责任报告》发布会在[[北京|北京]]举办。在本次发布会上，中铁集团发布了关于印尼高铁计划的官方宣传片。宣传片中提到该高铁项目将使用[[复兴号电力动车组|复兴号電力動車組]]。而根據宣傳片中的片段來看，極有可能將使用[[CR400AF型电力动车组|CR400AF電力動車組]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=印尼雅万高铁跑出新速度，中国智造闪耀“一带一路”|url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_10873379|accessdate=|author=|date=2021-01-21|format=|publisher=澎湃新闻|language=|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204030630/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_10873379|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=CREC Open Day — Proyek Kereta Cepat Jakarta-Bandung di Indonesia|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Q5NcLlSGmI&feature=youtu.be|accessdate=|author=|date=2021-01-21|format=|publisher=Youtube|language=印度尼亞語|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130201306/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-Q5NcLlSGmI&feature=youtu.be|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

